text: Wonsees is a municipality in Kulmbach in Bavaria in Germany. ==City arrangement== Wonsees is arranged in the following boroughs: * Feulersdorf * Gelbsreuth * Großenhül * Kleinhül * Lindenmühle * Plötzmühle * Sanspareil * Schirradorf * Wonsees * Zedersitz ==References== Category:Kulmbach (district)
title: Wonsees
